data.description: Discover the hidden potential in this 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom gem located in the highly desirable Trenholm Hills neighborhood. If you're searching for a project to customize and make your mark, this is the opportunity you've been waiting for. With a little TLC, this home can shine, offering endless possibilities for renovation and personalization. Inside, you'll find three bedrooms awaiting your creative touch, providing the canvas for your dream spaces. The bathroom, though functional, is ready for a stylish upgrade to suit your preferences. Situated on a generous lot, the property offers ample space for outdoor activities, gardening, or even an extension of the home. Trenholm Hills is known for its excellent schools, strong sense of community, and easy access to parks, shopping, and dining. This property is an investor's dream, with the potential to add significant value through renovation, convenience is at your doorstep. Priced to sell, this home represents a rare find in Trenholm Hills, making it an excellent investment opportunity. Don't let this chance slip away; this valuable property in Trenholm Hills won't last long. Schedule a viewing today and turn this house into your ideal home or a profitable venture!
